SAG-AFTRA To Hold Massive, Star-Studded Rally In Times Square On Tuesday Morning

SAG-AFTRA will hold a mass rally in Times Square on Tuesday morning. It’s expected to be the biggest rally in NYC since the strike began on July 14.
